  "title": "Quantity Surveyor (HDB/Condo/Landed Projects)",
  "description": "<ul><li>Assist in preparing bills of quantities, cost estimates, and tender documentation.</li><li>Monitor project expenditures and provide regular cost reports.</li><li>Review and evaluate subcontractor claims and variations.</li><li>Support senior QS in contract administration.</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Diploma/Degree in Quantity Surveying or equivalent</li><li>At least 3 years’ quantity surveying experience in <strong>HDB, Condo, and Landed projects.</strong></li><li>Knowledge of construction costing, contract management, and procurement.</li><li>Proficiency in cost management software and reporting tools.</li></ul><p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in<strong> MS Word </strong>to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p><p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p><p>EA Licence: 19C9701</p><p>Registration: R1326740</p>",
